Description:
    Generates a new stimulus controller. Pass the controller name, either
    CamelCased or under_scored.

    To create a controller within a module, specify the controller name as a
    path like 'parent_module/controller_name'.

    This generates a controller class in app/assets/javascripts/controllers.

Example:
    `bin/rails generate stimulus Message`

    Message controller
        Controller: app/assets/javascripts/controllers/message_controller.js
